This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with facial performances and image generation. It could also belong to graphics (cs.GR) as it involves animating characters. Multimedia (cs.MM) is another possible sub-category as it deals with video generation. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as the paper uses Generative Adversarial Network.
